CustomField.description: LEM-2734: Based on the terms of an MSA, Franchisees may be able to select Marketplace services they do not want their stores enrolled in. This field captures the services a Franchisee has deselected, and these services are not provisioned for all stores owned by the Franchisee.

CustomField.label: Deselected Marketplace Offerings
